@(1-13=c131.F.1) @wDN{Enki} spoke to the minister @wDN{Isimud}: @q[Enki,Isimud]{“@wDN{Isimud}, my minister, my Sweet Name of Heaven!” @q[Isimud,Enki]{“@wDN{Enki}, my master, I am at your service! What is your wish?” @q[Enki,Isimud]{“Since she said that she would not yet depart from here for @wSN{Unug} @wSN{Kulaba}, that she would not yet depart from here to the place where Utu ……, can I still reach her?” But holy @wDN{Inana} had gathered up the divine powers and embarked onto the Boat of Heaven. The Boat of Heaven had already left the quay. As the effects of the beer cleared from him who had drunk beer, from him who had drunk beer, as the effects of the beer cleared from Father @wDN{Enki} who had drunk beer, the great lord @wDN{Enki} turned his attention to the …… building. The lord looked up at the @fsux{abzu}. King @wDN{Enki} turned his attention to @wSN{Eridug}.

